author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Sparebank 1 BV Q4 Net Interest Income Nok 144.2 ‍​ Million Versus Nok 104.2 Million Year Ago
text:
Feb 9 (Reuters) - SPAREBANK 1 BV :
* Q4 NET INTEREST INCOME NOK 144.2 ‍​ MILLION VERSUS NOK 104.2 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 NET PROFIT NOK 118.2 MILLION VERSUS NOK 37.1 MILLION YEAR AGO
* Q4 REVERSAL LOAN LOSSES NOK 7.4‍​ MILLION VERSUS LOAN LOSSES NOK 5.9 MILLION YEAR AGO
* PROPOSES DIVIDEND FOR 2017 OF NOK 2.40 (1.87) PER EQUITY CERTIFICATE Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
